      <h2 style="margin-top:56px">SCSEP partnership with Goodwill Industries</h2>
      <p>The Caring Place partners with Goodwill Industries on the Senior Community Service Employment Program (SCSEP) — an on-the-job training and employment program for individuals aged 55 and older looking to update job skills and build experience.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:16px"><strong>Available SCSEP roles include:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Secretarial assistance</li>
        <li>Crisis hotline support</li>
        <li>Grounds keeping assistance</li>
      </ul>
      <p style="margin-top:20px">To learn more about SCSEP positions, contact Sharon Lavengood, Program Manager at Goodwill Industries: 574-276-9995 or <a href="mailto:slavengood@goodwill-ni.org">slavengood@goodwill-ni.org</a>.</p>

      <div class="callout" style="margin-top:44px">
        <p>The Caring Place is an equal opportunity employer, committed to employment without regard to race, religion, color, sex, age, ethnicity, national origin, disability status, sexual orientation, gender identity or expression, marital or family status, veteran status, or any other characteristic protected by law.</p>
